  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00001",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "柳梦梅上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00002",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "待我展开，观玩一番。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00003",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "二郎神",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "能停妥，这慈容只合在莲花宝座。咦，为甚独立亭亭在梅柳左？吓，不栽紫竹，边傍不放鹦哥。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00004",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "原来不是观音。哪！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00005",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "二郎神",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "只见两瓣金莲在裙下托。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00006",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "吓，是尊嫦娥！吓，又不像吓！我想既是嫦娥呵！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00007",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "二郎神",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "并不见祥云半朵。嗳，也非是嫦娥。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00008",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "既不是观音，又不是嫦娥，喂，难道人间女子不成？",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00009",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "二郎神",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "吓哈哈哈！这画蹊跷，教人难揣难摩。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00010",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "呀呸！只管胡思乱猜。看帧首之上，有小字数行，待我看来。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00011",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "“近睹分明似俨然，远观自在若飞仙。他年得傍蟾宫客，不在梅边在柳边。”",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00012",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "吓！原来人间女子的行乐图。吓！何言不在梅边在柳边呢？啊呀，真乃奇哉怪事也！",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00013",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "集贤宾",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "蟾宫哪能得近她？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00014",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "唔，",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00015",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "集贤宾",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "怕隔断天河。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00016",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "美人，你有此容貌，怕没个好对头，为甚傍柳依梅去寻结果？",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00017",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "想天下姓柳、姓梅的，却也不少，偏偏小生么，叫做柳梦梅。若论起梅边，小生是有份的；那柳边么，啊呀呀呀，也是有份的㖸！",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00018",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "集贤宾",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "喜偏咱梅柳停和。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00019",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "看这美人，有些熟识得紧，曾在哪里会过一次的，怎么一时再也想不起？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00020",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "集贤宾",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "我惊疑未妥。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00021",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "吓，",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00022",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "集贤宾",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "似曾向何方会我。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00023",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "吓，我想起来了！记得去春，曾得一梦，梦一大花园，梅树之下，立着一位美人么，喏喏喏，就是她。她说柳生吓柳生，与俺有姻缘之分，发迹之期。喂，美人可是你说的？是也不是？阿呀是也不是吓！",
      "text_length": 89
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00024",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "集贤宾",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "你休见左，敢则是梦中真个？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00025",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "唔！待我仔细认她一认，唵！看这美人，半枝青梅在手，却似提掇小生一般。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00026",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "莺啼御林",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "她青梅在手诗细哦，逗春心一点蹉跎。小生待画饼充饥，姐姐似望梅止渴。她未曾开半点么荷。咦！她含笑处朱唇淡抹。",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00027",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈！看这美人，这双俊俏的眼睛，只管顾盼着小生。小生走到这边，喏喏喏，她也看着小生。待我走到那边，咦咦咦！哈哈！她又看着小生。啊呀美人！你何必只管看着我，何不请下来相叫一声？吓美人，请吓，请请请吓！呀呸！柳梦梅呀，你好痴也！",
      "text_length": 112
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00028",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "莺啼御林",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "晕情多，如愁欲语只少口气儿呵！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00029",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "小娘子，你画似崔徽，诗如苏蕙，行书逼真卫夫人也。小生虽则典雅，怎及得小娘子万分之一？蓦地相逢，不免步韵一首：",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00030",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "“丹青妙处欲天然，不是天仙即地仙。”",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00031",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "唔，地仙，竟竟竟是地仙！哈哈！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00032",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "“欲傍蟾宫人近远，恰如春在柳梅边。”",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00033",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "岭南柳梦梅熏沐敬和。吓小娘子，这是小生的拙作，少不得么，还要请教，啊呀，还要请教㖸！",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00034",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "簇御林",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "她题诗句，声韵和，猛可的害相思颜似酡。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00035",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "啊，不是这等，待我狠狠的叫她几声。喂美人！小娘子！小姐，啊呀，我那姐姐吓！",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00036",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "簇御林",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "向真真啼血你知么？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00037",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "莫怪小生，",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00038",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "簇御林",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "我叫，叫得你喷嚏一似天花唾。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00039",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "咦！下来了。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00040",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "簇御林",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "嗳，动凌波。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00041",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "请坐㖸。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00042",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "簇御林",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "盈盈欲下，",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00043",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "呀呸！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00044",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "簇御林",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "全不见些影儿哪。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00045",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "吓小娘子，小生孤单在此，少不得将小娘子的画像，做个伴侣，早晚么，玩之，叫之，拜之，赞、赞、赞之！",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00046",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "尾声",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "俺拾得个人儿先庆贺。敢柳和梅有些瓜葛？美人吓！只被你有影无行盼煞我。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00047",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "吓小娘子，这里有风，请到里边去。唷，小娘子是客，自然小娘子先请，小生么，随后。唵，请吓！请请请吓！阿呀来㖸！哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902113_e00048",
      "play_id": "70902113",
      "scene_id": "70902113_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "柳梦梅下。",
      "text_length": 5
    }
